"3. Copy the jar file into the folder you want to use as the home folder for InternTrackr.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":10,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"4. Open a terminal, `cd` into that folder, and run:","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":11,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":12,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"   ```","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":13,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"   java -jar InternTrackr.jar","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":14,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"   ```","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":15,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":16,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"5. Type commands and press Enter to execute.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":17,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":18,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"Some commands you can try:","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":19,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2020-05-24T00:51:04","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":20,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"- `help` : Shows help.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":21,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"- `add c/\"Shopee\" r/\"Backend Intern\"` : Adds a new application.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":22,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"- `list` : Lists all applications.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":23,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"- `status 1 s/\"Interview\"` : Updates status of application 1.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":24,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"- `exit` : Exits the app.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":25,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":26,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"Refer to the [Features](#features) section below for details.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":27,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2020-05-24T00:51:04","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":28,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"## Features","lastModifiedDate":"2020-05-24T00:51:04","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":29,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2020-05-24T00:51:04","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":30,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"\u003e **Notes about the command format:**","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":31,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"\u003e","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":32,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"\u003e - Words in `UPPER_CASE` are parameters to be supplied by you.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":33,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"    \u003e   - Example: in `add c/COMPANY`, `COMPANY` can be `add c/\"Shopee\"` ...","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":34,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"\u003e - Items in square brackets are optional.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-10T09:46:15","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":35,"author":{"gitId":"N-SANJAI"},"content":"    \u003e   - Example: `deadline add ID t/TYPE d/DATE [n/NOTES]`","lastModif